            bindings = <
&none  &kp F1   &kp F2   &kp F3   &kp F4   &none                        &none        &none       &none       &none     &none     &none
&none  &kp F5   &kp F6   &kp F7   &kp F8   &none                        &kp TILDE    &kp PLUS    &kp EQUAL   &kp LBKT  &kp RBKT  &none
&none  &kp F9   &kp F10  &kp F11  &kp F12  &none                        &kp GRAVE    &kp UNDER   &kp MINUS   &kp LBRC  &kp RBRC  &none
